This is a stub of a Mikrotik TCP bwtest client.

Usage: Mikrotik_BandwidthTest.py [options] HOST

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -p PORT, --port=PORT  
  -t DURATION, --time=DURATION
                        test duration in seconds
  -m MTU, --mtu=MTU     
  -d DIRECTION, --direction=DIRECTION
                        test direction: receive, send, both
  -u USER, --user=USER  
  -a PASSWORD, --password=PASSWORD